# Summary
This documentation page details the setup and targeting options for guides in Amplitude, covering audience targeting (All Users vs Targeted Users), triggers (when and where guides appear), priority settings, display limits, guide statuses (Draft/Published/Schedule), and how the system handles active states and resolves conflicts when multiple guides are eligible for display.

